title: PrideFc-Final Conflict 2005.VOB
description: Which masters of the mixed martial arts will emerge triumphant in the final bouts of the 2005 Pride Fighting Championships? Find out in this hard-hitting two-disc collection of middleweight tournament matches, including Wanderlei Silva vs. Ricardo Arona, Mauricio "Shogun" Rua vs. Alistair Overeem, and bonus fights such as David "Tank" Abbott vs. Hidehiko Yoshida, and many more.
